{"tid":1338894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗係廢過中共。但而家唔係時間搞元朗","createTime":"2019-07-21T14:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:10:55.000Z","uid":89974,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fb8f9cd5ff98932f844c692d0cd68de33b97d8","tid":1338894,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"只要未解決警黑勾結，同埋警察不作為，光復元朗=沙包俾人打到仆街仲要比人拉<br />\n<br />\n只要打贏主線，我地每個禮拜入去光復都玩撚死作地，再用政府制度逼哂佢地啲非法利益出嚟，暗地裡再報串取消哂佢仔女國籍，到時佢地一反對就係警察對黑社會，今日佢地幾風流他日就幾咁折墮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總而言之，打贏主線=打贏支線，而家雙線齊開就比人打到豬頭"},{"pid":"715947feae2adac0e9ae3339b461cf6629c3ba56","tid":1338894,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f669b0dca45ffa87e46df417f9cbd55728afafa","tid":1338894,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3054ee7344e6079cc6109cbf7511d075ee8a0ddd","tid":1338894,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e09c3dc50002bb9b7fedf788cd029f30228b92ee","tid":1338894,"uid":19260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"元朗係d人返屋企會被圍打<br />\n所以元朗人返屋企前小心<br />\n或者去其他地方暫避"},{"pid":"2ddd8bdc099fb779affdb3439a8120d7773293a9","tid":1338894,"uid":269681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"有無念過支線係主線d怪整出黎 唔清左支線點推主線"},{"pid":"0b73372874ef0a216021d1df2bb08374c84c415b","tid":1338894,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"［支線］黑社會打人，黑警唔理，必須追究&rdquo;黑&rdquo;&rdquo;警&rdquo;聯盟，光復元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1338897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1338897</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac4995c5555b4b9682c6cd748860060523f0d9cf","tid":1338894,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e09c3dc50002bb9b7fedf788cd029f30228b92ee","